## Exit codes

- `0` — verdict `ship`
- `1` — verdict `revise` (or `ship` with `--ci` and any warnings)
- `2` — verdict `reject`

## When to use this skill

- Before merging an agent / skill change.
- In CI on any PR that touches `.claude/`.
- During a {{periodicity}} sweep of the team's roster.

## Anti-patterns

- Treating the linter's output as authoritative without reading the evidence.
- Ignoring `warning`-severity findings — they are the leading indicators.
- Auto-applying suggested fixes without a diff review.

